What are you talking about?

544
00:33:40,700 --> 00:33:42,000
It's a bigger loss for me.

545
00:33:42,000 --> 00:33:44,660
You know I've been single since birth. This would be my first kiss.

546
00:33:44,660 --> 00:33:46,980
So why would you do it?

547
00:33:46,980 --> 00:33:48,480
Can't you see them?

548
00:33:48,480 --> 00:33:51,900
Actions speak louder than words.

549
00:33:51,900 --> 00:33:54,800
- Just three seconds.
- Hey!

550
00:33:56,870 --> 00:34:00,460
Kiss! Kiss!

551
00:34:28,800 --> 00:34:31,310
Hey, smile.

552
00:34:31,310 --> 00:34:33,530
I said smile.

553
00:34:44,400 --> 00:34:45,920
They're kissing.

554
00:34:45,920 --> 00:34:47,670
That looks like the doe-eyed hottie.

555
00:34:47,670 --> 00:34:48,670
It is him.

556
00:34:48,670 --> 00:34:51,390
So, they were kissing?

557
00:34:54,560 --> 00:34:56,500
What is this?

558
00:34:58,780 --> 00:35:01,210
Is that what it was?

559
00:35:14,980 --> 00:35:16,460
Welcome.

560
00:35:16,460 --> 00:35:18,870
Take a seat over there.

561
00:35:26,020 --> 00:35:29,790
Could I get one portion civil servant udon noodles?

562
00:35:29,790 --> 00:35:32,020
