583
00:37:30,810 --> 00:37:32,650
Hi.

584
00:37:33,520 --> 00:37:34,800
Hey... you...

585
00:37:34,800 --> 00:37:37,720
You didn't expect to see me here, huh?

586
00:37:37,720 --> 00:37:41,410
Yeah. What are you doing here?

587
00:37:46,510 --> 00:37:48,760
The udon place lady told me.

588
00:37:48,760 --> 00:37:50,590
She said you would be here.

589
00:37:50,590 --> 00:37:52,390
Oh, that lady.

590
00:37:52,390 --> 00:37:55,480
Yeah, I come here often,

591
00:37:55,480 --> 00:37:57,850
because it's quiet here.

592
00:37:57,850 --> 00:38:00,660
How did you find the udon place lady, though?

593
00:38:00,660 --> 00:38:03,140
She seemed really popular on the online café for civil servant examinees.

594
00:38:03,140 --> 00:38:05,900
She has been touted as the president of Noryangjin.

595
00:38:05,900 --> 00:38:07,880
That's right.

596
00:38:07,880 --> 00:38:09,740
Are you preparing for the exam, too?

597
00:38:09,740 --> 00:38:12,860
No, I signed up to find you.

598
00:38:12,860 --> 00:38:14,440
Me?

599
00:38:15,400 --> 00:38:19,290
We didn't exchange numbers when we met last time.

600
00:38:19,290 --> 00:38:23,550
I've been really curious about how you were doing.

601
00:38:31,940 --> 00:38:33,760
Type in your number.

602
00:38:35,410 --> 00:38:37,560
You're not married, are you?

603
00:38:37,560 --> 00:38:39,740
- No.
- Or about to get married?

604
00:38:39,740 --> 00:38:42,170
Having kids is okay.

605
00:38:46,410 --> 00:38:49,910
You're still your wild self, Kim Jihye.

606
00:38:54,010 --> 00:38:55,800
Here it is.

607
00:39:00,600 --> 00:39:02,710
It's ringing.

608
00:39:08,810 --> 00:39:12,990
We laughed a lot together when we were in school.

609
00:39:13,910 --> 00:39:16,150
I think I laughed my fill back then.

610
00:39:18,360 --> 00:39:21,460
I'm still super funny.

611
00:39:21,460 --> 00:39:23,220
Huh?

612
00:39:23,220 --> 00:39:24,900
The day after a company dinner,

613
00:39:24,900 --> 00:39:29,670
people take a sick day because their stomachs hurt from laughing.

614
00:39:29,670 --> 00:39:31,370
They take a sick day?

615
00:39:31,370 --> 00:39:33,610
Because their stomachs hurt?

616
00:39:35,050 --> 00:39:36,080
It hurts!

617
00:39:36,080 --> 00:39:38,400
Gosh, seriously.

618
00:39:40,240 --> 00:39:42,520
You hit as hard as usual.

619
00:39:53,240 --> 00:39:55,590
Can I call you every once in a while?

620
00:39:56,470 --> 00:39:58,240
Sure.

621
00:39:58,240 --> 00:40:01,570
But there will be a lot of times when I won't be able to pick up.

622
00:40:01,570 --> 00:40:03,630
I'll call you back, though.

623
00:40:13,520 --> 00:40:17,010
