624
00:40:40,270 --> 00:40:42,110
What's this?

625
00:40:46,990 --> 00:40:49,690
Smoking isn't good for your health, so don't do it too much~!

626
00:40:49,690 --> 00:40:51,630
From Jihye.

627
00:40:54,510 --> 00:40:57,190
Gosh, that wild girl.

628
00:41:23,470 --> 00:41:25,790
What is she doing?

629
00:41:30,810 --> 00:41:35,050
Should I just forget about everything and make him mine?

630
00:41:35,050 --> 00:41:36,470
No, Choi Yuri.

631
00:41:36,470 --> 00:41:38,240
That would make you a bad bitch.

632
00:41:38,240 --> 00:41:41,270
Jieun is struggling a lot right now.

633
00:41:42,620 --> 00:41:44,630
But...

634
00:41:46,770 --> 00:41:49,580
I'm struggling, too.

635
00:42:22,340 --> 00:42:24,350
So noisy.

636
00:42:24,350 --> 00:42:26,580
Let me sit with you.

637
00:42:30,020 --> 00:42:31,690
- Ma'am.
- Yes?

638
00:42:31,690 --> 00:42:34,610
A Coke and rolled eggs.

639
00:42:35,960 --> 00:42:38,960
- Also, some rice.
- Yes.

640
00:42:38,960 --> 00:42:40,930
What's up with you?

641
00:42:43,150 --> 00:42:46,200
Stop filling up with liquid. Eat some real food.

642
00:42:46,200 --> 00:42:48,810
You probably starved all day.

643
00:42:53,150 --> 00:42:54,780
Cheers.

644
00:43:23,840 --> 00:43:25,770
What's all this?

645
00:43:30,960 --> 00:43:33,800
Hey, what is this? What's going on?

646
00:43:34,790 --> 00:43:36,260
World War 29.

647
00:43:36,260 --> 00:43:38,920
Dad bought stocks behind Mom's back.

648
00:43:38,920 --> 00:43:40,220
What's so bad about that?

649
00:43:40,220 --> 00:43:42,760
