650
00:43:42,760 --> 00:43:45,620
He apparently lost 30 million won (~$30,000).

651
00:43:45,620 --> 00:43:47,680
What's this? This is Dad's.

652
00:43:47,680 --> 00:43:50,410
It was sitting outside.

653
00:43:52,000 --> 00:43:53,800
Seriously.

654
00:44:02,070 --> 00:44:03,880
First shelf of the living room bookcase.

655
00:44:03,880 --> 00:44:07,290
"The Know-Hows of an Expert on Getting Loved by His Wife"

656
00:44:07,290 --> 00:44:12,400
Page 78, page 88, page 98.

657
00:44:14,180 --> 00:44:16,590
78...

658
00:45:05,520 --> 00:45:07,860
Ma'am, could I have another glass?

659
00:45:07,860 --> 00:45:09,550
Yes.

660
00:45:11,160 --> 00:45:13,330
Gosh, Dad.

661
00:45:14,260 --> 00:45:16,230
Straighten your shoulders.

662
00:45:16,230 --> 00:45:19,210
A man can get into stocks at some point.

663
00:45:19,210 --> 00:45:20,820
It happens.

664
00:45:20,820 --> 00:45:23,630
You only lost 30 million, not 300 million.

665
00:45:23,630 --> 00:45:25,410
It was 50 million.

666
00:45:25,410 --> 00:45:27,230
50 million?

667
00:45:28,800 --> 00:45:31,130
You worked for the government all your life.

668
00:45:31,130 --> 00:45:32,980
Why play stocks now?

669
00:45:32,980 --> 00:45:37,210
You told me not to touch money if I don't work for it.

670
00:45:37,210 --> 00:45:39,740
You told me that so many times.

671
00:45:50,010 --> 00:45:52,150
What do I do?

672
00:46:00,660 --> 00:46:02,260
Go home.

673
00:46:06,730 --> 00:46:08,040
Dad.

674
00:46:08,040 --> 00:46:09,650
Let's just go home.

675
00:46:09,650 --> 00:46:11,180
No, no.

676
00:46:11,180 --> 00:46:13,980
I need to stay away tonight.

677
00:46:14,960 --> 00:46:17,290
I'm sorry...

678
00:46:17,290 --> 00:46:21,260
that you had to see your dad in this state.

679
00:46:24,270 --> 00:46:26,040
Go.

680
00:46:38,910 --> 00:46:40,920
Welcome.

681
00:46:57,730 --> 00:47:02,370
Do you know what life and soju have in common?

682
00:47:02,370 --> 00:47:06,340
Nuna, you haven't even had a single shot of soju.

683
00:47:07,500 --> 00:47:11,600
The common point is that...

684
00:47:14,130 --> 00:47:16,330
they both have two syllables!

685
00:47:17,250 --> 00:47:19,540
Should I just leave you and go?

686
00:47:21,980 --> 00:47:27,330
I had my first-ever kiss today.

687
00:47:27,330 --> 00:47:30,660
But that kiss was not the beginning.

688
00:47:30,660 --> 00:47:33,010
It was the end. The end.

689
00:47:33,010 --> 00:47:35,960
If you were going to cover for him, doing it that decisively was the best way.

690
00:47:35,960 --> 00:47:39,250
I also sensed

691
00:47:39,250 --> 00:47:41,740
that Yunjae and Jihun had that kind of relationship.

692
00:47:41,740 --> 00:47:45,010
But that was my first kiss.

693
00:47:47,720 --> 00:47:50,160
- Is it a problem that it was your first?
- Of course!

694
00:47:50,160 --> 00:47:52,020
The first one is so important.

695
00:47:52,020 --> 00:47:55,570
I wouldn't be acting like this if it were my second or third.

696
00:48:02,500 --> 00:48:04,390
This is not love.

697
00:48:04,390 --> 00:48:06,450
This is fandom.

698
00:48:29,140 --> 00:48:30,950
That crazy...

699
00:48:30,950 --> 00:48:32,050
Follow me.

700
00:48:32,050 --> 00:48:35,680
What? Nuna, why are you being like this?

701
00:48:35,680 --> 00:48:37,850
I'm not ready for that yet.

702
00:48:37,850 --> 00:48:40,910
That's Park Yunjae, right?

703
00:48:43,600 --> 00:48:45,720
Yunjae?

704
00:48:45,720 --> 00:48:48,780
Why is he going in there?

705
00:48:48,780 --> 00:48:51,470
- Is he with Jihun?
- He went to his mom's shop earlier.

706
00:48:51,470 --> 00:48:52,990
Then?

707
00:48:54,030 --> 00:48:56,820
I stayed up all night, thanks to you.

708
00:48:56,820 --> 00:48:58,180
What's with you?

709
00:48:58,180 --> 00:49:02,410
Yesterday, you told me I was pretty.

710
00:49:03,840 --> 00:49:05,220
It has to be Kang Minju.

711
00:49:05,220 --> 00:49:07,260
- Who?
- Kang Minju.

712
00:49:07,260 --> 00:49:09,610
She has a crush on Yunjae.

713
00:49:09,610 --> 00:49:12,650
He went to a motel with her?

714
00:49:12,650 --> 00:49:14,770
I knew something was off.

715
00:49:14,770 --> 00:49:16,380
Why? What is?

716
00:49:16,380 --> 00:49:17,510
Is he cheating?

717
00:49:17,510 --> 00:49:20,230
I mean they asked each other how they slept.

718
00:49:20,230 --> 00:49:22,490
"Yesterday, you told me I was pretty."

719
00:49:22,490 --> 00:49:24,530
Saying stuff like this.

720
00:49:38,350 --> 00:49:40,150
- Mom.
- Yeah?

721
00:49:40,150 --> 00:49:43,130
Could you teach me how to cut hair?

722
00:49:44,130 --> 00:49:45,320
What do you need that for?

723
00:49:45,320 --> 00:49:49,530
I mean... It's not like I can get a job while I'm a guy.

724
00:49:49,530 --> 00:49:52,460
I thought I could learn at your shop.

725
00:49:52,460 --> 00:49:55,710
Yes, Honey. That sounds like a good idea.

726
00:49:55,710 --> 00:49:58,640
You think anyone can be a hairdresser?

727
00:49:58,640 --> 00:50:01,360
You're not even good with your hands.

728
00:50:01,360 --> 00:50:04,420
That's why I'm asking you to teach me.

729
00:50:16,640 --> 00:50:18,630
What's up, Yuri?

730
00:50:19,440 --> 00:50:21,980
Me? I'm at my mom's shop.

731
00:50:23,250 --> 00:50:26,370
Yunjae? I talked to him earlier. Why?

732
00:50:26,980 --> 00:50:30,220
What? Motel?

733
00:50:30,220 --> 00:50:32,130
Who did you say he went with?

734
00:50:46,880 --> 00:50:50,770
Where is he? Where is Park Yunjae?

735
00:50:50,770 --> 00:50:52,180
Did he really go in with Kang Minju?

736
00:50:52,180 --> 00:50:53,970
That's what I'm telling you.

737
00:50:54,600 --> 00:50:58,990
Hyeong, hi. I'm sorry we're seeing each other like this.

738
00:50:58,990 --> 00:51:02,290
How could Park Yunjae do this to me?

739
00:51:02,290 --> 00:51:04,430
Call him right now.

740
00:51:05,450 --> 00:51:07,250
It's Yunjae!

741
00:51:14,440 --> 00:51:19,040
He was wearing a jacket earlier, but now it's gone.

742
00:51:20,990 --> 00:51:23,540
What a bastard.

743
00:51:23,540 --> 00:51:25,580
I can't hold back.

744
00:51:25,580 --> 00:51:27,840
Hey, Park Yunjae!

745
00:51:27,840 --> 00:51:31,080
Hey, hi. What are you doing here?

746
00:51:31,080 --> 00:51:32,880
What? Hi?

747
00:51:32,880 --> 00:51:36,370
You just got caught red-handed, yet you're acting so brazen.

748
00:51:37,230 --> 00:51:40,090
Hey, Kim Jieun! Come out!

749
00:51:44,360 --> 00:51:47,850
Hey, what's going on with you guys?

750
00:51:47,850 --> 00:51:50,050
Jihun, why are you here?

751
00:51:50,050 --> 00:51:54,390
We saw everything. We saw you enter and exit the motel.

752
00:51:54,390 --> 00:51:58,360
It's been an hour, seven minutes and thirty-four seconds.

753
00:52:00,000 --> 00:52:02,750
You were evem timing it?

754
00:52:02,750 --> 00:52:05,150
Did you go with Minju?

755
00:52:06,160 --> 00:52:08,890
Did you go with Kang Minju?

756
00:52:08,890 --> 00:52:10,810
What are you...?

757
00:52:12,210 --> 00:52:14,680
I went with my dad.

758
00:52:14,680 --> 00:52:20,010
Dad? Hey, why not just say you went with your mom?

759
00:52:23,600 --> 00:52:26,470
I get how this situation could lead to a misunderstanding,

760
00:52:26,470 --> 00:52:30,140
but I really came with my dad.

761
00:52:30,140 --> 00:52:31,470
Lead the way.

762
00:52:31,470 --> 00:52:33,300
- That's right.
- What?

763
00:52:33,300 --> 00:52:35,610
If you're so confident, lead the way.

764
00:52:35,610 --> 00:52:37,490
There you go!

765
00:52:38,210 --> 00:52:39,640
Do you really want to do this?

766
00:52:39,640 --> 00:52:42,230
I have nothing more to lose.

767
00:52:42,230 --> 00:52:45,320
You'll have to come to my house to tutor.

768
00:52:47,490 --> 00:52:49,990
That's not what's important right now.

769
00:52:49,990 --> 00:52:52,580
You're hilarious today.

770
00:52:52,580 --> 00:52:53,900
Let's go.

771
00:52:53,900 --> 00:52:56,620
- Hey, follow me.
- Huh?

772
00:53:05,610 --> 00:53:08,760
Nuna, I think it's overkill for us to go, too.

773
00:53:08,760 --> 00:53:10,660
Park Yunjae is the one who went overboard.

774
00:53:10,660 --> 00:53:12,550
Hurry up and follow me.

775
00:53:16,840 --> 00:53:19,340
Hey. Look carefully.

776
00:53:19,340 --> 00:53:20,980
Will do.

777
00:53:22,960 --> 00:53:24,790
Dad.

778
00:53:28,070 --> 00:53:30,030
Dad!

779
00:53:36,420 --> 00:53:37,570
Who are you?

780
00:53:37,570 --> 00:53:39,890
I see. You must be Kang Minju.

781
00:53:39,890 --> 00:53:41,410
No, no.

782
00:53:41,410 --> 00:53:43,600
What's going on?

783
00:53:44,550 --> 00:53:48,340
I'm sorry. I had the wrong room number.

784
00:53:48,340 --> 00:53:50,010
Gosh.

785
00:53:50,010 --> 00:53:51,810
Sorry.

786
00:53:56,370 --> 00:53:58,330
No, it's the room next door.

787
00:53:58,330 --> 00:54:01,370
Room next door, my foot. Open the door now!

788
00:54:03,370 --> 00:54:04,970
It's really the room next door!

789
00:54:04,970 --> 00:54:07,450
I had the wrong room number.

790
00:54:07,450 --> 00:54:09,110
Follow me.

791
00:54:13,950 --> 00:54:15,730
Look now.

792
00:54:18,470 --> 00:54:20,330
Dad?

793
00:54:22,550 --> 00:54:24,230
Dad.

794
00:54:24,230 --> 00:54:27,970
You're so absent-minded. You left your jacket here.

795
00:54:31,860 --> 00:54:33,860
Look, it's my dad.

796
00:54:33,860 --> 00:54:36,130
My dad!

797
00:54:36,130 --> 00:54:38,700
It's my dad!

798
00:54:38,700 --> 00:54:41,900
My dad! Guys, look. It's my dad.

799
00:54:41,900 --> 00:54:43,890
- Guys, my dad.
- Hello.

800
00:54:43,890 --> 00:54:45,910
My dad.

801
00:54:47,520 --> 00:54:51,050
See? It's not Kang Minju.

802
00:54:51,050 --> 00:54:53,380
Dad.

803
00:54:53,380 --> 00:54:55,690
I'm sorry.

804
00:54:55,690 --> 00:54:59,020
Nuna. Nuna, where are you going?

805
00:55:04,370 --> 00:55:06,530
Let's go. It's okay.

806
00:55:27,770 --> 00:55:29,930
I'm a bit upset.

807
00:55:30,750 --> 00:55:33,410
Never mind the others.

808
00:55:33,410 --> 00:55:36,180
I didn't expect you would doubt me.

809
00:55:36,180 --> 00:55:38,210
I'm sorry.

810
00:55:38,210 --> 00:55:41,360
I kept telling myself there's no way,

811
00:55:41,360 --> 00:55:43,740
but Yuri was so sure about it.

812
00:55:44,840 --> 00:55:47,290
I had no idea you had so little trust in me.

813
00:55:47,290 --> 00:55:50,540
If only I didn't see you with Kang Minju like that—

